headline: High-Performance Supercomputer Launched to Advance AI Innovation and Scientific Discovery
summary: Equinix, Inc. (Nasdaq: EQIX), the world's digital infrastructure company®, today announced Merck KGaA, Darmstadt, Germany, a leading science and technology company, has successfully launched a state-of-the-art high-performance computer (HPC) built on Lenovo ThinkSystem servers with industry-leading liquid cooling technology. The HPC is hosted within an Equinix AI-ready data center in Germany and has been designed to accelerate innovation across the three business sectors of Merck KGaA, Darmstadt
